<item>
            <title>[SPARK-1629] Spark should inline use of commons-lang `SystemUtils.IS_OS_WINDOWS` </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-1629</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Right now we use this but don&apos;t depend on it explicitly (which is wrong). We should probably just inline this function and remove the need to add a dependency.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
